snippet.title: These two female tourists had no idea that their vacation would turn into a nightmare
snippet.description:
These two female tourists had no idea that their vacation would turn into a nightmare

Tragedy strikes Stephanie and Ellie when the latter goes missing while on a bike trip. Things take a turn when Stephanie enlists the help of a stranger to look for Ellie.

Movie: And Soon the Darkness
Year of Release: 2010
Production companies: Priority Pictures
Watch the full movie here: https://www.amazon.com/Soon-Darkness-Amber-Heard/dp/B004HGSRYO

Thank you for watching.
